column1: @catgeyser No! Please call or email my office and get on the list. But it’s not clear what form the event will take. 🤷‍♂️ #COVID19

I miss person-to-person campaigning that happens in the days before the election. I loved it today when the server put his hand on my shoulder like he’s my old pal and says “you got my vote buddy.” #COVID19 #vote
My sister has been a school nurse but via #covid staffing adjustments she’s now assigned to teach PE online. This is worth a view. We never appreciate teachers enough! https://t.co/eTGTs0Tfrw
@GilCabrera Peter Navarro calling out Tony Fauci on COVID strategy on national TV is peak Trump Administration.

Also please hold in your hearts two of my friends  @StevePadillaCV and @willrk787 who are in tough battles with #COVID19 tonight. This is not a drill. Keep your distance wash hands and stay in as much as possible.

Showing the new selfie protocol with social distancing. #TeamPeters showed up to hand out food with @sdlaborcouncil - we will keep you up to date with how you can help. Follow my office Twitter @RepScottPeters #coronavirus https://t.co/cKPA4STIPQ https://t.co/X8UipgERlF
